### Invites — Create invite link, accept invite

### Create invite (by email or shareable link)
### Copy inviteToken from response into http-client.env.json
POST {{host}}/api/invites
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "partner@example.com"
}

###

### Accept invite (run as the invited user after they register/login)
POST {{host}}/api/invites/{{inviteToken}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
